# React Language Selector
This is the langpack picker/switcher that will be used in all BitShares POS systems. It's written in React.js with JSON (no more jquery!). 
 
<b>Please vote, it helps me fund these apps!</b><br>
Open BitShares wallet > Advanced > Console: approve delegate.kencode true 

<link href="stylesheets/react-language-selector-ui.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="javascripts/react-with-addons-0.13.3.min.js"></script>
<!-- language specific code -->
<script src="javascripts/react-simplehtmlparser.min.js"></script>
<script src="javascripts/react-language-selector.min.js"></script>
<!-- language specific code -->

<div ng-controller="DemoController" style="display: inline">
    <div id="rlsui1"></div>
</div>
